title: 10 Takeaways from Week 15
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 15
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Rhett Lewis and Bucky Brooks are back to give their Week 15 takeaways, including the 49ers heartbreaking loss to the Falcons (1:00), the Cowboys beatdown of the Rams (4:50), Carson Wentz and Eagles win in the end (8:40), the Vikings defense dominating the Chargers (11:40), Jameis Winston roller coaster ride continues for Bucs (15:40), Texans one step closer to AFC South crown (21:10), the Bills clinching a playoff spot with win over Steelers (25:20), the Patriots turned it on in Cincinnati (29:10), Kyler Murray’s win over college teammate Baker Mayfield (32:50), Eli Manning goes out in New York as a winner (35:55).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
